text: Kampong Wasan is a village in Pengkalan Batu, a mukim in Brunei-Muara District, Brunei. The postcode for Kampong Batu Ampar is BH2523. == Name == Kampong Wasan is derived from the same name in Malay which translates as 'Wasan Village'. == References == Wasan Category:Brunei-Muara District
title: Kampong Wasan
